AS if Appearing on America's Got Talent: The Champions was
not enough, the talented DJ Arch Junior is remixing Eminem’s song Monckingbird. The youngster recently got a standing ovation on America's Got Talent:
The Champions. One of the judges, Simon Cowell even said he has plans for the DJ. After he finished with his performance Cowell said: “You
and I need to be talking after this show because I’ve got some plans for you,
trust me. I think you are a total little star, I absolutely love you.
What a way to start the show; you are everything that this show is all about,
thank you” he said. DJ Arch Junior shot to fame when he won SA’ Got Talent in 2015. 